<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 12:34:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗战争推高油价，比特币跟随股市上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/bitcoin-drops-to-7-day-low-as-oil-surges-on-iran-war-concerns</link><description>尽管对伊朗长期战争的担忧日益加剧，导致油价飙升、股市和债券暴跌，但比特币仍在上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iii.3pbxed8E/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 02:49:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/bitcoin-drops-to-7-day-low-as-oil-surges-on-iran-war-concerns</guid></item><item><title>稳定币支付公司 KAST 筹集 8000 万美元资金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/stablecoin-payments-firm-kast-raises-80-million-in-funding</link><description>随着风险投资家继续向提供数字美元账户的初创公司注入资金，稳定币支付公司 KAST 在最新一轮融资中筹集了 8000 万美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/if2Fu7zdU0Fk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 09:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/stablecoin-payments-firm-kast-raises-80-million-in-funding</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的世界自由金融项目让投资者陷入困境</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-08/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-project-puts-investors-in-a-bind</link><description>特朗普家族的旗舰加密项目再次面临质疑。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iybdDrNO3uIU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-08/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-project-puts-investors-in-a-bind</guid></item><item><title>随着伊朗冲突持续，加密货币市场追踪战争风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/crypto-markets-track-war-risk-as-iran-conflict-endures</link><description>加密货币市场再次成为交易者如何定价中东持续冲突的唯一开放窗口，随着伊朗战争进入第二周，Hyperliquid 上跟踪石油、黄金和白银的合约显示出显着的走势。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0qzdRvR17UY/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 14:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/crypto-markets-track-war-risk-as-iran-conflict-endures</guid></item><item><title>稳定币公司在几乎不存在的人工智能代理支付上押下重注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/stablecoin-firms-bet-big-on-ai-agent-payments-that-barely-exist</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc. 和 Stripe Inc. 正在竞相为一个尚不存在的世界构建支付系统——在这个世界中，自主人工智能代理每天进行数百万次交易，以稳定币结算，而不是刷信用卡。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJiLirZFi0gc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/stablecoin-firms-bet-big-on-ai-agent-payments-that-barely-exist</guid></item></channel></rss>